Package: white-list-monitor
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyqt6, python3-requests, python3-apscheduler, iputils-ping
Maintainer: LiberVixer <sophia.wilson.99@outlook.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/LiberVixer/WhiteListMonitor
Description: GUI monitor for whitelist-mode VPN candidate analysis
 White List Monitor is a Linux desktop utility for monitoring restricted
 network modes, collecting VPN subscription candidates, rating them for
 whitelist-like environments, and exporting ready-to-use top server lists.
